---
title: Sirloin Steak & Creamy Truffle-Mushroom Sauce with Chive Mash & Roasted Rainbow Carrots
description: Who says that steak and mash can't be gourmet? When you top tender beef with a silky mushroom sauce flavoured with truffle oil and add creamy mashed potato flecked with chives, this classic combo gets a restaurant-quality vibe. Pour yourself a glass of something special and prepare for a fine dining experience.
